languages.text: "Кому ты тут заливаешь! Чего бы {mf|Его|Ее} Светлости тут делать? Чего просить благословленн{mf|ому|ой} самим Богом-Императором у обычных смертных, пусть даже в дворце закона? Стой в очереди как все, {mf|толстосум|богатейка}, и не смей порочить имя Вольного Торговца!"

languages.text: "Who do you think you're kidding? What would {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship} be doing here? What would one of the God-Emperor's anointed need from ordinary mortals, and in a palace of the law to boot? Queue like everybody else, {mf|Master|Mistress} Moneybags, and do not disgrace the Rogue Trader's name again!"

languages.text: “得了吧！你唬谁呢？如果{mf|他|她}真是这么有权有势的人，还排什么队啊？得到神皇赐福的人，怎么会跑到我们这种平头老百姓来的地方？赶紧和其他人一样好好排着去吧，装腔作势的家伙！别再给行商浪人的名字抹黑了！”

languages.text: «¿A quién pretendes engañar? ¿Qué iba a hacer aquí su señoría? ¿Qué iba a necesitar un{mf|o|a} de los elegidos del Dios Emperador de los meros mortales, y más en un palacio de la ley? ¡Ponte a la cola como todos los demás, ricach{mf|ón|ona}, y no vuelvas a deshonrar el nombre de{mf|l| la} Comerciante Independiente!».

Queue like everybody else, {mf|Master|Mistress} Moneybags, and do not disgrace the Rogue Trader's name again!"

languages.text: 「俺を誰だと思ってバカ言ってるんだ？陛下が何でここに来るんだよ。凡人とはほど遠い神帝陛下の任命を受けた方が、おまけに法務宮殿だって？他のみんなと同じく並べよ、金持ちの{mf|マスター|ミストレス}、二度と自由開拓者の名を騙るなよ！」
languages.original_text: "Who do you think you're kidding? What would {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship} be doing here? What would one of the God-Emperor's anointed need from ordinary mortals, and in a palace of the law to boot? Queue like everybody else, {mf|Master|Mistress} Moneybags, and do not disgrace the Rogue Trader's name again!"

traits.speaker: AdministratumQueueMemberM1

languages.text: « Je regrette, mais ça ne prend pas. Qu'est-ce que Sa Seigneurie viendrait faire ici, hein ? Les représentants consacrés de l'Empereur sont exemptés des lois et formalités administratives applicables au commun des mortels. Faites la queue comme tout le monde, espèce de {mf|parvenu|parvenue}, et ne vous avisez plus jamais de déshonorer le nom {mf|du libre-marchand|de la libre-marchande} ! »
languages.original_text: "Who do you think you're kidding? What would {mf|His Lordship|Her Ladyship} be doing here? What would one of the God-Emperor's anointed need from ordinary mortals, and in a palace of the law to boot? Queue like everybody else, {mf|Master|Mistress} Moneybags, and do not disgrace the Rogue Trader's name again!"

languages.text: "Wer soll das glauben? Was sollte {mf|Seine Lordschaft|Ihre Ladyschaft} denn hier wollen? Was braucht jemand, den der Gottimperator gesalbt hat, von gewöhnlichen Sterblichen, noch dazu in einem Palast des Gesetzes? Stellt Euch an wie alle anderen, {mf|Herr|Herrin} Geldsack, und entehrt nicht noch einmal den Namen {mf|des Freihändlers|der Freihändlerin}!"

languages.text: "Bizimle dalga mı geçiyorsunuz yahu? {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri'nin burada işi ne? Tanrı İmparator'un bizzat kutsadığı insanlardan birinin bizim gibi sıradan fânilerden ne ihtiyacı olabilir ki. Hele bir de bir kanun sarayında? Siz de herkes gibi kuyruğa girin bakalım {mf|sahip|sahibe} efendi, bir daha da Hür Tacir'in adına leke süreyim demeyin!"
